data.description: Back on the market not due to listing or sellers fault. This home welcomes you with great curb appeal boosting one of a kind design of brick and vinyl siding with a walk-in front porch. Located in a well-established neighborhood! Walk in to an open floor plan and enjoy the cozy living area with wood burning fire place and kitchen/dining area with plenty of cabinet space. Oversized master bedroom and bathroom, fenced-in Back Yard, 2 car garage and so much more! Inspection is done and all repairs were made for your type of loan! New roof being installed. Take advantage of this opportunity!!  Call to schedule your private showing today before it is GONE!
